{"_path":"/blog/en/mountains-of-poland","_dir":"en","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Autumn and winter in the mountains of Poland","description":"When I moved to the Netherlands I knew that this country is known of many beautiful places: old towns of Amsterdam, Leida and Haarlem, windmills located by rivers and lakes, endless beaches on the coast of the North Sea. I knew, however, that it lacks mountains and I knew I am going to miss them. I kept tiring my friends with stories about the Netherlands being flat.","published_at":"2021-01-24","intro":"Once our one-year-long trip aboard s/y Moonshine was over I spent few months in Poland. Previous time I spent so much time at home was over four years ago - before I moved to the Netherlands. After four year I missed not only my family and friends, but also Polish mountains.","category":"photography","background":"v1620583199/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-19_omepn9.jpg","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"When I moved to the Netherlands I knew that this country is known of many beautiful places: old towns of Amsterdam, Leida and Haarlem, windmills located by rivers and lakes, endless beaches on the coast of the North Sea. I knew, however, that it lacks mountains and I knew I am going to miss them. I kept tiring my friends with stories about the Netherlands being flat."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Coming back to Poland I decided to spent some time in the mountains. I always carried my camera the backpack but sometimes there was no reason to take it out. The reason was the autumn and winter weather - volatile, full of rain and fog. But once the sun shines it's easy to fall in love with Tatras, Pieniny, Beskids and Karkonosze. Below I show a collection of photos taken recently."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"70","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583197/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-1_ha62gq.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ View from Trzy Korony (Three Crowns) in Pieniny."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"133","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583197/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-2_cfzz68.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ Swans at dawn. Brzeszcze, Małopolska."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"75","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583197/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-3_cvcki1.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ Lakes in Nazieleńce from a bird's eye view."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"126","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583197/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-4_dtfnsw.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ Siklawa waterfall (in Western Tatras) lit by the full moon."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.6","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583197/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-5_nvzbur.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ Sunrise on Wołowiec: view on the Ridge of Rohacze."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.6","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620