osze: frozen trees on the way to Śnieżka."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"134.5","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583198/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-16_ajyq7u.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ A view from Śnieżka to Dom Śląski mountain shelter."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.66","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583199/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-17_bvunmy.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ Volatile conditions in Karkonosze: in just few minutes sunny weather can become a dense fog."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"150","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583198/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-18_clwbx1.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ A metre of snow and wind blowing all the time create wonderful ice sculptures in Karkonosze."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"62.5","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583199/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-19_omepn9.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ View on Tatry and Gorce from a trail to Turbacz."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.6","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583199/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-20_c8njp0.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ Sunset on a trail in Gorce."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"150","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583199/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-21_ks4rw5.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ Sunset in Gorce."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"photo-lazy","props":{"padding":"66.6","src":"https://res.cloudinary.com/lukaszrados/image/upload/v1620583199/stories/mountains-of-poland/w-polskich-gorach-22_fgub7y.jpg"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"em","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"▲ Mountain shelter on Turbacz after sunset."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"During these three months in Poland I managed to go hiking 11 times and walk 160 km. Few of those were just quick trips for a sunrise or sunset while some were a full day long trips. Many of them ended up being miserable and bringing no photos but sometimes it was hard to stop taking photos. Most of all it was a great way to escape locked down cities."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"More photos of Polish mountains can be found in my gallery - "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/photography/poland-mountains"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Poland - Mountains"}]},{"type":"text","value":"."}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:blog:en:mountains-of-poland.md","_source":"content","_file":"blog/en/mountains-of-poland.md","_extension":"md"}